author: USA TODAY, Jesse Yomtov, USA TODAY
title: US now has more coronavirus deaths than any other country, but the worst of epidemic may not be far off
description: The U.S. has suffered more fatalities from the coronavirus than any other country, including Italy, which has been an epicenter.
content:
As the COVID-19 pandemic continues, Americans wonder if the illnesses they had earlier this year were actually a result of the novel coronavirus.
